  <Strings>
    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45216</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_024_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ねぇ、そう言えば、アルベルトって、ぼくたちと一緒に
食事してるけど、食べた物ってどうなってるの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Um, Albert? There's something I wanted to ask you for a while. You've had dinner with us before but how do you actually eat the food?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45332</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_024_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>お、それ、オレも気になってた！
扉開けても、服しか出てこねーしな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hey! That's right! It's been bothering me too! We've opened you several times but all we see is clothes!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45400</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_024_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>クリュールゥ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kuruu?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45544</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_024_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>まぁ、おめぇらの薄っぺらい脳みそで考えたところで、
ぜぇーったいわかるわけがねぇーだーよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Well, you have to consider your brains are extremely small. We don't really expect you to understand ANYTHING.</EnglishText>
      <Notes>name issue</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45680</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_024_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>う～ん……わたしたちよりいっぱい食べてるのに、
どこに行ってるのか不思議だよね……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Mister Albert... We were wondering if you'd be so kind to reveal us the secret where the food you eat goes....</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45824</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_024_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Mel&gt;&lt;Mel&gt;が、おらに興味を持ってるなら、教えるだよ。
実は、おらの体の中というのは……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Since &lt;Mel&gt;-&lt;Mel&gt; asked so kindly I'll reveal this wondrous secret! Let me tell you. What really is inside my body is...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45892</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_024_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>いうのは……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Is...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45984</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_024_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>体の中というのは…………実は…………</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Inside my body...actually...is...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46072</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_024_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>…………おらにもよくわからねぇだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I don't have the slightest idea.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46136</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_024_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>なにソレ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What the...!?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46260</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_024_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ひとつだけ確かなのは、腹が減ったら、
何か食べたくなるってことだ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The only thing I'm sure of is that food passes through my stomach and I...well, eat.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
